            "title": "A股個別發展   深股向上",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">A股個別發展。滬股跌深股報升。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬綜指開報3328，跌4點或0.12%，現報3331點，跌0.48點或0.01%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深成指報10616，跌10點或0.09%，現報10667，升40點或0.38%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300開報3900，跌5點或0.13%，現報3906，升1點或0.05%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">創業板指數開報2176，平開，現報2190，升14點或0.68%。</p>\n</div>",
